        "Confirm the crane or hoist certification, inspection, capacity, setup, and operator requirements.",
        "Identify overhead power lines, public areas, traffic, hoarding, scaffolds, and adjacent trades.",
        "Assign the rigger, signal person, operator, spotters, and landing crew.",
