    "summary": "Use this page when demolition, renovation, strip-out, structural removal could involve hazards or outcomes such as uncontrolled collapse, hazardous materials, dust exposure, utilities, public interface. It gives supervisors and crews a plain-language starting point for the controls, documents, and stop-work triggers that should be checked before work starts.",
