        "Define the exact task, location, workers, equipment, materials, and expected duration.",
        "Read [[site-emergency-response-plan|Site Emergency Response Plan]] and the site procedure before setting up the work.",
        "List the hazards and possible outcomes, including fire, collapse, gas release, medical emergency, blocked exit, and identify everyone who could be affected.",
        "Confirm the official source, owner/client requirement, manufacturer instruction, and site rule that apply. {{cite:ohsr-part-32}}",
        "Prepare or update the required document set, including evacuation procedure.",
